summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $57.50 from the general fund of the City of Seattle to pay the cost of redelivery bonds in suits of E. B. Brendel v. C. L. Beckingham, et al, Cause No. 115534, Ralph Boyker, doing business as the Northern Drug Company v. the City of Seattle, a municipal corporation, Cause No. 115631; and People's Pharmacy, a corporation, v. C. L. Beckingham, et al, Cause No. 115533, and directing the city comptroller to issue warrants therefor.
